title: No 10 Year rewards
body: Hey, Just wondering why I haven't received the rewards. Thanks for your time!

replies.body:
It looks like you may have already gotten the Summoner Icon, but we're still sending out the rest of gifts until the 30th, as *Zombiemaster* mentioned.

Let me know if you don't have it after the 30th.

The gifts are still being distributed as per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us). The final day to receive them has been moved to the 30th. Just hand tight and you will receive them soon enough! :)
